*[[1938]] &amp;ndash; [[Constantin Stanislavski]], Russian/Soviet [[theatre practitioner]] (b. 1863)
*[[1941]] &amp;ndash; [[Rabindranath Tagore]], Indian author, [[Nobel Prize in Literature|Nobel Prize Laureate]] (b. 1861)
