*  1970   &amp;ndash; [[Jonathan P. Jackson|Jonathan Jackson]], instigator of the [[Marin County courthouse incident|Marin County Civic Center shootout]] and brother of [[Black Panthers|Black Panther]] [[George Jackson (Black Panther)|George Jackson]] (b. 1953)
