*[[1972]] &amp;ndash; [[Andrea Feldman]], American actor (b. 1948)
*[[1973]] &amp;ndash; [[Dean Corll]], American serial killer (b. 1939)
*  1973   &amp;ndash; [[Vilhelm Moberg]], Swedish author and historian (b. 1898)
*  1973   &amp;ndash; [[Nikos Zachariadis]], General Secretary of the [[Communist Party of Greece]] (b. 1903)
*[[1974]] &amp;ndash; [[Baldur von Schirach]], Nazi youth leader (b. 1907)
*[[1975]] &amp;ndash; [[Julian &quot;Cannonball&quot; Adderley]], American jazz saxophonist (b. 1928)
*[[1977]] &amp;ndash; [[Edgar Adrian, 1st Baron Adrian]], British electrophysiologist; [[Nobel Prize in Physiology or Medicine|Nobel Prize Laureate]] (b. 1889)
*[[1979]] &amp;ndash; [[Nicholas Monsarrat]], British novelist (b. 1910)
*[[1980]] &amp;ndash; [[Paul Triquet]], French Canadian army officer (b. 1910)
*[[1982]] &amp;ndash; [[Eric Brandon]], British racing driver (b. 1920)
*[[1984]] &amp;ndash; [[Ellen Raskin]], American author (b. 1928)
*[[1985]] &amp;ndash; [[Louise Brooks]], American actress (b. 1906)
*[[1987]] &amp;ndash; [[Danilo Blanuša]], Croatian mathematician (b. 1903)
*[[1988]] &amp;ndash; [[Félix Leclerc]], Quebec singer and songwriter (b. 1914)
*  1988   &amp;ndash; [[Alan Napier]], English actor (b. 1903)
*[[1991]] &amp;ndash; [[Julissa Gomez]], American gymnast (b. 1972)
*  1991   &amp;ndash; [[James Irwin]], astronaut (b. 1930)
*[[1992]] &amp;ndash; [[Grand Ayatollah]] [[Abu al-Qasim al-Khoei]], Iranian religious figure (b. 1899)
*  1992   &amp;ndash; [[John Kordic]], Canadian ice hockey player (b. 1965)
*[[1995]] &amp;ndash; [[John Adams (running back)|John Adams]], American football player (b. 1937)
*[[1996]] &amp;ndash; [[Nevill Francis Mott]], British physicist; [[Nobel Prize in Physics|Nobel Prize Laureate]] (b. 1905)
*[[1998]] &amp;ndash; [[Mahmoud Saremi]], Iranian journalist
*[[2004]] &amp;ndash; [[Fay Wray]], American actress (b. 1907)
*  2004   &amp;ndash; [[Dimitris Papamichael]], Greek actor (b. 1934)
*[[2005]] &amp;ndash; [[Barbara Bel Geddes]], American actress (b. 1922)
*  2005   &amp;ndash; [[Ahmed Deedat]], Islamic scholar (b. 1918)
*  2005   &amp;ndash; [[John H. Johnson]], African-American publisher (b. 1918)
*  2005   &amp;ndash; [[Gene Mauch]], American baseball player (b. 1925)
*  2005   &amp;ndash; [[Dean Rockwell]], American wrestling and football coach (b. 1912)
*  2005   &amp;ndash; [[Monica Sjöö]], Swedish artist (b. 1938)
*  2005   &amp;ndash; [[Ilse Werner]], German actress (b. 1921)
*[[2007]] &amp;ndash; [[Joybubbles]], A notable phone phreak. (b. 1949)
*  2007   &amp;ndash; [[Ma Lik]], Chinese politician (b. 1952)
*  2007   &amp;ndash; [[Melville Shavelson]], American film director, producer, and screenwriter (b. 1917)
*[[2008]] &amp;ndash; [[Orville Moody]], American golfer (b. 1933)
*  2008   &amp;ndash; [[Leonard Pagliero]], British stationer (b. 1913)
*[[2009]] &amp;ndash; [[Daniel Jarque]], Spanish footballer (b. 1983)
*[[2010]] &amp;ndash; [[Patricia Neal]], American actress (b. 1926)
